## Catalog metadata

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Report file | `GitHub-Scanner-{{ target.repo }}.md` (+ `.html` companion) |
| Repo | [github.com/{{ target.owner }}/{{ target.repo }}]({{ target.url }}) |
| Short description | {{ catalog.get('short_description', repo_meta.get('description', '')) }} |
| Category | `{{ catalog.get('category', '') }}` |
| Subcategory | `{{ catalog.get('subcategory', '') }}` |
| Language | {{ repo_meta.get('primary_language', '') }} |
| License | {{ repo_meta.get('license_spdx', 'None') }} |
| Target user | {{ catalog.get('target_user', '') }} |
| Verdict | **{{ verdict }}**{% if should_split %} (split — see below){% endif %} |
| Scanned revision | `main @ {{ short_sha(head_sha) }}` (release tag `{{ latest_tag }}`) |
| Commit pinned | `{{ head_sha }}` |
| Scanner version | `{{ scanner_ver }}` |
| Scan date | `{{ scan_date }}` |
| Prior scan | {{ prior }} |

